LABEL: 0x84
JPN: バッグの隅から出てきた。
ENG: I found it stuffed into the corner of my bag.

LABEL: 0xac
JPN: クラブの練習用に買ってもらった、防水多機能腕時計。
ENG: It was a multi-functional waterproof wristwatch I bought to use in my club.

LABEL: 0xee
JPN: 無意識に遠ざけていたけど、最近はプールに入る機会も出てきたし、使えるかもしれない。
ENG: I'd sort of been ignoring it up until that point, but since I was spending a fair bit of time in a pool again, I figured it might be useful.

LABEL: 0x206
JPN: 居間に来るなり、声を掛けられる。
ENG: Kyouko-san called out to me as I walked into the living room.

LABEL: 0x268
ENG: "Someone called for you just a moment ago."

LABEL: 0x3ac
JPN: 「俺がこっちで悪さしないか気になってるんでしょう」
ENG: "I bet she was worried I was causing trouble."

LABEL: 0x4a0
JPN: 「鏡子さんは、知ってますよね」
ENG: "Kyouko-san, you know about all that stuff, right?"

LABEL: 0x53e
ENG: "About how I got suspended from school."

LABEL: 0x5aa
JPN: 「学校の配慮で夏休みとかぶってますけど……一応、謹慎中なんですよね、俺」
ENG: "They were nice enough to suspend me over the break, but... I'm supposed to be staying at home right now, really."

LABEL: 0x61c
ENG: "I've more or less heard all about it."

LABEL: 0x6f0
JPN: 「夏休みって本来楽しいものですけど」
ENG: "I guess summer vacations are supposed to be fun, so no surprise there."

LABEL: 0x80e
ENG: "Yeah, one of them kinda looks like this."

LABEL: 0x8b2
JPN: 「そうです、私が変な友達です……」

LABEL: 0x9d0
JPN: 「あぁ、さっき来てくれたんだよ」
ENG: "Ahh, she arrived just a moment ago."

LABEL: 0xa7a
ENG: "I'm here to return something you forgot..."

LABEL: 0xad2
JPN: しろはは、手に釣り竿を持っていた。
ENG: Shiroha was carrying a fishing pole.

LABEL: 0xb04
ENG: "I actually found that on the ground, myself..."

LABEL: 0xc92
JPN: とても何かを言いたげだ。
ENG: She looked like she really wanted to ask me something.

LABEL: 0xcda
JPN: あんな話を聞いてしまっては。
ENG: I mean, considering what she just overheard.

LABEL: 0xd06
JPN: 「気になるなら、聞いて良いよ」
ENG: "Feel free to ask, if you're curious."

LABEL: 0xdf8
ENG: "Wait, that's what you were curious about!?"

LABEL: 0xe30
JPN: てっきり停学について突っ込まれるのかと思ったら、予想外なところに質問が飛んできた。
ENG: Her question caught me completely off guard. I was sure she wanted to ask about my suspension.

LABEL: 0xe92
JPN: さっき部屋で見つけて、つけた時計が気になっていたらしい。
ENG: I guess she was more curious about the watch I found in my room.

LABEL: 0xeda
JPN: 「停学とかの方は気にならないのか」
ENG: "You don't wanna ask about why I'm suspended, and stuff?"

LABEL: 0xff6
JPN: 「売ってるところ教えてあげたいけど」
ENG: "I'd tell you where to get one, but..."

LABEL: 0x1034
JPN: 「限定モデルなんだ。世界で５０だけの」
ENG: "It's a limited edition. There's only fifty in the world."

LABEL: 0x1130
JPN: 「大会で優勝したときに買って貰ったんだ」
ENG: "It was a present they got for me 'cause I won a tournament."

LABEL: 0x11f0
JPN: すごくなんてない。何も。
ENG: There's nothing impressive about it. Nothing at all.

LABEL: 0x124a
JPN: なんでまた、腕時計を凝視しているのか。
ENG: She was staring at the watch again, for some reason.

LABEL: 0x12b0
ENG: "Um... So, what do you mean by suspension?"

LABEL: 0x12e8
JPN: ついでに、という感じで触れてきた。
ENG: She finally broached the subject in an 'oh, by the way' sort of manner.

LABEL: 0x137c
ENG: "You got suspended and ran away from home."

LABEL: 0x13d2
JPN: 並べられると、けっこう壮絶だ。
ENG: It actually sounded pretty crazy, when she put it that way.

LABEL: 0x14ca
JPN: いきなりしろはが、必死になった。

LABEL: 0x150a
JPN: 「そんなの、すごく心配してるよ」

LABEL: 0x15a4
JPN: 『知ったようなこと言うなよ』なんて……その必死な表情を見たら言えなかった。
ENG: Part of me wanted to tell her off for assuming she knows my parents better than I do... But with how serious she looked, I couldn't bring myself to say it.

LABEL: 0x163c
JPN: 「……ほらでも、まだいろいろとやらないといけないことがあるし」
ENG: "...But I've still got a bunch of stuff I've gotta do here, though."

LABEL: 0x16da
ENG: "Like sorting through the shed, and stuff."

LABEL: 0x173c
JPN: 「かなりね。俺、鏡子さんの右腕みたいなものだから」
ENG: "Yeah. I'm basically Kyouko-san's right-hand man right now."

LABEL: 0x1804
JPN: なんでいきなりアクティブなんだ。
ENG: Where's this proactive side of her coming from?

LABEL: 0x1834
JPN: 「そんなに俺を帰したいのか」
ENG: "Do you want to send me home that much?"

LABEL: 0x18a2
JPN: あっさりとした返事だった。
ENG: She replied without a hint of hesitation.

LABEL: 0x18cc
ENG: "Okay, but I still can't go home."

LABEL: 0x19a2
ENG: "I've still gotta teach you how to swim."

LABEL: 0x1a84
ENG: "You don't have to worry about me."

LABEL: 0x1ace
JPN: 俺にはそうは、思えなかった。
ENG: It didn't seem that way to me.

LABEL: 0x1b2e
JPN: 「ちょっと気になってたんだ」
ENG: "There's something I've been kind of curious about."

LABEL: 0x1b64
JPN: 「しろははなんで泳げるように、がんばってるんだ」
ENG: "Why are you so dead set on learning how to swim?"

LABEL: 0x1bee
JPN: 「それは……泳げた方がいいに決まってるから」
ENG: "Well... Because knowing how to swim's better than not knowing, obviously."

LABEL: 0x1c62
ENG: "But still, I kinda get the feeling that, like..."

LABEL: 0x1c8c
JPN: 「しろはって、別に泳ぎたいわけじゃないような気がして」
ENG: "You're not trying to learn because you want to."

LABEL: 0x1cdc
JPN: 「何か理由があったんじゃないの」

LABEL: 0x1d16
ENG: "Something more than just wanting to swim."

LABEL: 0x1d48
JPN: 「泳げなくちゃいけないような理由が」
ENG: "Something that gives you no choice but to learn how to swim."

LABEL: 0x1de8
JPN: 「それは、もしかしたらしろはの言ってた……」

LABEL: 0x1e2e
JPN: 「呪いとかに関係してるのかなって」
ENG: "Is it related to that curse thing you talked about?"

LABEL: 0x1ecc
JPN: 思いつきで言ってみたものの……
ENG: I only mentioned it in passing.

LABEL: 0x1efa
JPN: しろはの反応を見る限り、当たらずしも遠からずといった様子だ。
ENG: Still, her reaction told me I wasn't exactly right, but not that far off either.

LABEL: 0x1ff2
JPN: 「しろはが、泳げるようになったら」
